[Distinguish between short and long help again
david@lichteblau.com**20081029150934
 
 --help now extremely short, showing only easy, reliable commands
 
 --long-helps includes all the exotic commands for experts
 
 In particular, don't show options like "build" which are bound to
 fail compiling a test suite here and there.  Don't mention the
 possibility of installing --all-projects are similarly hairy operations.
